author: Greg P.
title: Guess which daughter of a former president is the keynote speaker at Planned Parenthood fundraiser
text:
— Maeve Reston (@MaeveReston) February 24, 2017 
Bet you weren’t expecting this… Barbara Pierce Bush, the daughter of former President George W. Bush, will headline a Planned Parenthood fundraiser: https://t.co/npSpqb7EoH pic.twitter.com/XdnC23ODIk 
— Texas Tribune (@TexasTribune)   BOOHOO: CNN releases smarmy statement about being blocked from White House media gaggle 
From the article: 
Barbara Pierce Bush, the daughter of former President George W. Bush, will headline a Planned Parenthood fundraiser in North Texas on Wednesday. 
She will be the keynote speaker at Planned Parenthood of Greater Texas’ annual Fort Worth luncheon, helping to raise money for an organization that provides an array of reproductive and sexual health services, including abortions. 
Bush’s public appearance before the group is striking, given that her father, President George W. Bush , was a staunch abortion opponent during his time as Texas governor and as president. 
Flashback: Barbara attended a fundraiser for Hillary Clinton in Paris last year: She had also been spotted at a Hillary Clinton fundraiser in Paris, but nbd https://t.co/cebpHSIRUE 
— Abby D. Phillip (@abbydphillip) February 24, 2017
